// make map, with starting map pixels
	// each pixel specifies
		1) color
		2) type (permanent, destroyable)
		3) projectile blocking v non-blocking
		4) player blocking v non-blocking

// make stage over the top of the map.
	Include objects on stage that
		1) are subject to physical laws
			1) gravity
			2) friction
			3) collisions
			4) gun kickback
		2) Can detect collisions 
			1) with other objects
			2) with map
		3) Can alter speed and aim.
		